name: The Right Move
overview:
Over 20 years of providing moving services, The Right Move have been here for all moving requests. Packing things and moving preparations are very stressful. Imagine how it is to carry those big loads of heavy furniture and equipment with no help at all! Definitely, Houston Moving can help! We pack, store, pick- up and deliver.

The Right Move provides local, country and interstate relocation, commercial moves, packing services, storage, insurance and other moving services such as pet, car and boat transport, unpacking and water bed service. Call us today and see what The Right Move can do for you!
